{"tid":1570363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「擊中大陸春袋」《人民日報》微博稱在國土唱國歌才是共享的榮光","createTime":"2019-09-15T04:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:04:42.000Z","uid":152455,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef3343f6d2d8de8959bd172d4bad97bca47f6bf","tid":1570363,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />敵人緊張了，證明我方做對了，分裂力量狀大係大陸最唔想接受既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日有市民響應網上號召，到淘大花園商場，唱國歌及揮動國旗，另一批市民就在同一地點，唱反修例歌曲，兩批人士相遇後發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n人民日報在微博發表評論，表示近日香港市民唱國歌被打傷，引來了更多愛國愛港者齊聚，自豪高歌愛國歌曲，又說愛國從不孤獨，正義不應沉默。<br />\n<br />\n評論又表示，某些勢力妄圖營造的恐怖氣氛，不過是螳臂當車，改變不了香港屬於中國的事實，更改變不了大多數香港人的那顆中國心，又說在自己國家的土地上舉國旗、唱國歌，才是值得中國人共享的榮光。"},{"pid":"6915e350cca80f927fed2aa580c780106e69f775","tid":1570363,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"我想問，而家牆內係咪禁播榮光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879ba2cc61ef5fede6c53c10a21d2dc088ee89c3","tid":1570363,"uid":68598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"咁係人地國家唱算唔算宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2ce4e768be5a1b5271c97c060ed5c60b239850","tid":1570363,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6915e350cca80f927fed2aa580c780106e69f775","tid":1570363,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"我想問，而家牆內係咪禁播榮光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"r